During botanical fieldwork in November 2022 in limestone areas of Bac Kan Province in northern Vietnam, we collected several specimens sharing the above-mentioned generic characteristics of 

Ridsdalea

, but morphologically different from all species hitherto known by a number of unique characteristics. After consulting relevant literature (

